Column Name	    Data Type	    Description

id	            INT	            Unique identifier for the user (Primary Key)
username	    VARCHAR(50)	    Username for the user
email	        VARCHAR(100)	Email address of the user nullable
password	    VARCHAR(255)	Hashed password of the user
full_name	    VARCHAR(100)	Full name of the user
role	        VARCHAR(50)	    Role of the user (e.g., "admin", "manager", "employee", "user")
created_at	    TIMESTAMP	    Timestamp when the user account was created
updated_at	    TIMESTAMP	    Timestamp when the user account was last updated